      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like there's nothing left inside. for years the colors and the music were everything, but now it's just... gone. i look in the mirror and i don't see a person, i just see this hollow shell of a body. it's like the soul went out and left the house empty. it feels so pointless to just keep moving through the motions when the thing that made me \"me\" is dead.",
